  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/ef6afc7b6884ad204e3ea919463a6859.webp?t=1770668750\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press the Keyboard to attack and destroy electronic devices. <br><strong>Your keyboard is the battlefield. Your hands are the weapon.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/da284e498bbe98ce3703a25f349c85c2.poster.avif?t=1770668750\" width=602 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/da284e498bbe98ce3703a25f349c85c2.webm?t=1770668750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/38dccca79104bcaa186d32d046d2a4e6.webp?t=1770668750\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a keyboard warrior <br>with various attack-style keyboard axes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/95bef1fe271649dee244e98cb0e2706e.poster.avif?t=1770668750\" width=604 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/95bef1fe271649dee244e98cb0e2706e.webm?t=1770668750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/bea8db17e648b1b57f824440990491da.webp?t=1770668750\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cable, USB, mouse, etc. fight electronic devices that threaten the keyboard, <br>Show me what the best devices are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/f53de0d84d95e544601a99e7a04458a8.poster.avif?t=1770668750\" width=602 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/f53de0d84d95e544601a99e7a04458a8.webm?t=1770668750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/bec7a8fa208d80eedd4f1c6c423834a7.webp?t=1770668750\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get a keycap, get a new ability, get stronger. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/8063db7b9b8e4bae4b50567017055c28.poster.avif?t=1770668750\" width=602 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514910/extras/8063db7b9b8e4bae4b50567017055c28.webm?t=1770668750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
